score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"過去一個月，大家都進入戰爭狀態。即使無受傷、無被捕都好，精神一定都好攰好崩緊，需要好多休息。<br />\n所以我提議大家搞返民間放映會，地點盡量安排返啲街坊區，例如公園仔或者天橋，而唔係去咩遮打/維園。<br />\n一黎係啲街坊區搞嘅話方便大家落樓行幾步就到，慳返好多舟車勞頓嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二黎，街坊區搞放映會係最有效散播信息比我地以外嘅人。搞親中環/維園大集會，去親嘅都係同路人多。大家樓下播警暴嘅片先係最有效傳比啲普通人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於舉辦形式我建議兩種。<br />\n一種就咁帶口罩遮樣，拎住ipad / laptop 出黎，係天橋位播警暴嘅片。<br />\n我之前見過有兩位小妹妹，放學之後著住校服就咁帶住口罩拎個ipad粒聲唔出企係到播片。然後有好多師奶阿叔睇。<br />\n好處：<br />\n比較自由，就咁單拖落去播片就得，唔洗點籌備。你粒聲唔出淨企係到播片，其實啲街坊又唔會搞你，因為你又無搞事。好多阿伯反而無聊當睇展覽咁睇。<br />\n<br />\n唔好處： 萬一真係有咩人搞事或者有狗黎逗你就比較麻煩，少人幫手。<br />\n<br />\n第二個方法：<br />\n聯絡區議員一同舉辦放映會。如果大家唔敢單拖嘅話，我認為聯絡區議員一齊搞會比較好。始終有咩事區議員可以幫手，例如有狗個陣佢可以調停。<br />\n不過搵區議員幫手唔代表比晒佢搞，始終人地都忙，而且放映會又唔算太難搞。幫到手嘅咪一齊拎部ipad、laptop出黎一齊播片，或者借藍牙喇叭出黎。<br />\n<br />\n知道大家懶搵片，呢到有晒整合！<br />\n有個癲佬整合左612-115嘅黑警行兇證據呀！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696899</a> （借些牙 唔該巴打）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8d075a372dabca47bb22298c30a56b876894a3","tid":1765933,"uid":95588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b09991034dd2d6390d67fc7500b983a9e0deb07","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:46:24.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"607afa218660bcad89a02b92d10a76d2b7314693","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"今晚12點前上熱門<br />\n推比全世界人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7419bcbeb448149586bbd44858bd794af51be383","tid":1765933,"uid":129805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"認同呢類文宣野已經冇左最開頭個種熱誠，所以大家都要加油"},{"pid":"28b13392bba9b0abe31e95ebcb0c64f02f3b7192","tid":1765933,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d4a420ebb753e04e13c7de2d8a09361f00a2183","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:49:14.000Z","msg":"放映會真係唔難，幾個朋友約埋一齊拎個ipad落樓下公園仔、天橋播就得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜樓豬無朋友..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓豬想區議員招募義工後參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a8954e914da775690a3a230e18539d2395c122","tid":1765933,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf596ba10ebbd9ecd3e85d96923f977fe8ab39f","tid":1765933,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc530b5bbbbf70dc4c4667b95327f7e4e084f4a8","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7419bcbeb448149586bbd44858bd794af51be383","tid":1765933,"uid":129805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"認同呢類文宣野已經冇左最開頭個種熱誠，所以大家都要加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"啱啊 好多連儂牆都爛晒好耐都無人貼新<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div><br />\n唔怪得嘅，大家都有攰嘅時候，休息完繼續加油！"},{"pid":"a93e0df61b2507b94ceacc9737bdfc9a83a1a823","tid":1765933,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671050dd2a79050633a10cefb965998e6c436d30","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"大學呢幾日開始陸續開返啲<br />\n又係時候返去用quota print文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94162e045b04deac38402ec722219cb58c05d727","tid":1765933,"uid":10471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"819f603a39b654f7efb790f556797ba7751f8003","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:52:20.000Z","msg":"我要上熱門！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74250949117028648fb4c27e86bd58d1265113f0","tid":1765933,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:52:39.000Z","msg":"好啦咁"},{"pid":"78247daaa57b9f3e4f817ffe6a02aa97e3b77aa5","tid":1765933,"uid":149866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c8fc9a414b2afdddcd849a9cd2fc7b08fee605ef","tid":1765933,"uid":20076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d67d461983e7dc4985a4e3d6cd1fe809e76247f0","tid":1765933,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:53:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0770334f71bc2d496a27529c19e1661b281758a5","tid":1765933,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1355f45afcabbc4ea415366c1a8d4fa9a63c472","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"話說發覺我有兩個post比連仔del左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個講升級行動<br />\n一個講我屋企樓下有人用marker係公告欄唱鳩某室住戶係黑警"},{"pid":"c43a0a95fa433fd5134a5a368829b168a6b0a29c","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1355f45afcabbc4ea415366c1a8d4fa9a63c472","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"話說發覺我有兩個post比連仔del左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個講升級行動<br />\n一個講我屋企樓下有人用marker係公告欄唱鳩某室住戶係黑警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪收到投訴話我煽動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過連仔真係好過舊登林早洩好多<br />\n好似未見過連仔交人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ecf7c7aed83f3d49e64315e55a4357f417ecab7","tid":1765933,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e25b5d00db6257144d5de7e04e4ff83153af1654","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係區議員要睇到！<br />\n由區議員號召大家做義工幫手安全好多！<br />\n一黎唔驚係公海搵人搵著狗。<br />\n二黎有區議員坐陣唔緊比狗踩場。<br />\n三黎容易啲聚到人做野搞放映會。區議員有號召力啲，而且好似合法係啲大廈嘅𨋢放告示通知街坊有放映會。<br />\n區議員們唔洗擔心我地係咁點你做野，只係想你做下號召，因為如果普通人一個就咁講野宣傳真係無咩用。我相信區議員們一招募義工，大把手足拎ipad laptop 藍牙喇叭落嚟幫手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638dcb4e3990090c3186f4623bd8d2710ef18a7c","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"5fcf29bcc19a6f67619d1186d93a91f673d0fbd2","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c6ff8d0bc64aed77e096a1573eeddf4e619ee7e1","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:04:38.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"6e87099e9f781f7de8446e22daddc3a499cd226b","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d311f6e154a347bbfe8725e22aa7c2d3c71ee055","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"57f25795cb8f0d8c08f7916dc71bec53bd37aafc","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"6/10"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e25b5d00db6257144d5de7e04e4ff83153af1654","tid":1765933,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係區議員要睇到！<br />\n由區議員號召大家做義工幫手安全好多！<br />\n一黎唔驚係公海搵人搵著狗。<br />\n二黎有區議員坐陣唔緊比狗踩場。<br />\n三黎容易啲聚到人做野搞放映會。區議員有號召力啲，而且好似合法係啲大廈嘅𨋢放告示通知街坊有放映會。<br />\n區議員們唔洗擔心我地係咁點你做野，只係想你做下號召，因為如果普通人一個就咁講野宣傳真係無咩用。我相信區議員們一招募義工，大把手足拎ipad laptop 藍牙喇叭落嚟幫手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}